<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="6Dec1940"><font color="red">6 December 1940</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Carola Giedion-Welcker): Having read the letters enclosed and having communicated the contents to Ruggiero would you be good enough to send them immediately to M. Augsbourg at Villa El-Sol, Prilly, Lausanne? I hope that is his real address. I have written myself to M. Lester directly [re American Red Cross intervention for Lucia] &hellip; I received also on Monday a reply to a long telegram I sent to Vichy on Friday from Petitjean </div>
